Y KWOK 1 週前<br />\n🙏 儲水，儲糧 很重要。請大家 留心聽聽  世澤 兄的求生寶貴經驗 及分享給大家兄弟手足；我發覺 我們年輕一代缺乏「 危機感 」❤️🇭🇰❤️ </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Yan ng 1 週前<br />\n想留就留，想走就走啦。自己都唔爭氣，國際點幫我地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>angel wong 1 週前<br />\n最憎嗰班攻擊泛民既帳號, 又出賣又貪錢, 見到就煩 </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>TsuiAnn 1 週前<br />\n留咪留走咪走 兩者都無傷大雅<br />\n我覺得健康碼同國際新聞重要d </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>angel wong 1 週前<br />\n其實我係因為留任單野block左太多youtuber, 先搵到來呢度 <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Bebe Lee 1 週前<br />\n係到睇comment 真係好舒服🥰 <br />\n辛苦曬你 </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不能盡錄<br />\n黃世柒：我呢個channel既成就係靠我努力經營返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口罩錢就係洗係呢D地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a735601fdabc6efd9e5ad37e0dbced9ccd406ab","tid":2234734,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2873ab57c9c05be8262e4aa34695d59c8f4a7a4b","tid":2234734,"uid":32204,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:41:02.000Z","msg":"世柒佢審查完啲 comments 先放出街<br />\n你係唔會見到反對聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd4608edfbf3bfc62c0fa723705486349c13b9b","tid":2234734,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2873ab57c9c05be8262e4aa34695d59c8f4a7a4b","tid":2234734,"uid":32204,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy"